{"id":959,"parent_id":949,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":959,"title":"Zechariah 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"Zech.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","Judah and Joseph will be scattered among the people in far countries—The Lord will hiss for them, gather them, and redeem them."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.1","order":"02.39.010.63097"},["b","1"],"Ask ye of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"rain in the time of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"latter"],"rain;",["i","so"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall make bright clouds, and give them showers of rain, to every one grass in the field."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.2","order":"02.39.010.63098"},["b","2"],"For the idols have spoken vanity, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"diviners"],"have seen a lie, and have told false",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"dreams"],"; they comfort in vain: therefore they went their way as a flock, they were troubled, because",["i","there was"],"no",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"shepherd"],"."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.3","order":"02.39.010.63099"},["b","3"],"Mine anger was kindled against the shepherds, and I punished the goats: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts hath visited his flock the house of Judah, and hath made them as his goodly horse in the battle."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.4","order":"02.39.010.63100"},["b","4"],"Out of him came forth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"the corner"],", out of him the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"nail"],", out of him the battle bow, out of him every oppressor together."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.5","order":"02.39.010.63101"},["b","5"],"¶And they shall be as mighty",["i","men,"],"which tread down",["i","their enemies"],"in the mire of the streets in the battle: and they shall fight, because the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],["i","is"],"with them, and the riders on horses shall be confounded."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.6","order":"02.39.010.63102"},["b","6"],"And I will strengthen the house of Judah, and I will save the house of Joseph, and I will bring them again to place them; for I have mercy upon them: and they shall be as though I had not cast them off: for I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"their God, and will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"hear"],"them."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.7","order":"02.39.010.63103"},["b","7"],"And",["i","they of"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Ephraim"],"shall be like a mighty",["i","man,"],"and their heart shall rejoice as through wine: yea, their children shall see",["i","it,"],"and be glad; their heart shall rejoice in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.8","order":"02.39.010.63104"},["b","8"],"I will hiss for them, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"gather"],"them; for I have redeemed them: and they shall increase as they have increased."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.9","order":"02.39.010.63105"},["b","9"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"sow"],"them among the people: and they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"remember"],"me in far countries; and they shall live with their children, and turn again."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.10","order":"02.39.010.63106"},["b","10"],"I will bring them again also out of the land of Egypt, and gather them out of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Assyria"],"; and I will bring them into the land of Gilead and Lebanon; and",["i","place"],"shall not be found for them."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.11","order":"02.39.010.63107"},["b","11"],"And he shall pass through the sea with affliction, and shall smite the waves in the sea, and all the deeps of the river shall dry up: and the pride of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Assyria"],"shall be brought down, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"sceptre"],"of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"Egypt"],"shall depart away."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.12","order":"02.39.010.63108"},["b","12"],"And I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"strengthen"],"them in the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; and they shall walk up and down in his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"name"],", saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.1a","order":"02.39.010.63109"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/11.14"},"Deut. 11:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/2.23"},"Joel 2:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.2a","order":"02.39.010.63111"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/18.20"},"Deut. 18:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.2b","order":"02.39.010.63113"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dream"},"TG Dream"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.2c","order":"02.39.010.63115"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/shepherd"},"TG Shepherd"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.4a","order":"02.39.010.63117"},["b","4a"],["span.small","IE"],"the cornerstone.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/118.22.21-22"},"Ps. 118:22 (21–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/21.42.42-46"},"Matt. 21:42 (42–46)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.4b","order":"02.39.010.63119"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/22.23"},"Isa. 22:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.6a","order":"02.39.010.63121"},["b","6a"],["span.small","OR"],"answer."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.7a","order":"02.39.010.63123"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/48.14.14-22"},"Gen. 48:14 (14–22)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/64.36.33-36"},"D&C 64:36 (33–36)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.60.60-61"},"109:60 (60–61)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.32.16-35"},"133:32 (16–35)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.8a","order":"02.39.010.63125"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.9a","order":"02.39.010.63127"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/13.7.7-9"},"Zech. 13:7 (7–9)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-ten-lost-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Ten Lost Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.9b","order":"02.39.010.63129"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/30.2.1-3"},"Deut. 30:2 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.10a","order":"02.39.010.63131"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-ten-lost-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Ten Lost Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.11a","order":"02.39.010.63133"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.25"},"Isa. 14:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.11b","order":"02.39.010.63135"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/11.15"},"Isa. 11:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/30.13"},"Ezek. 30:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.11c","order":"02.39.010.63137"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/19.16.11-25"},"Isa. 19:16 (11–25)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.19"},"Joel 3:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.12a","order":"02.39.010.63139"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/31.8"},"D&C 31:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/37.2"},"37:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/zech/10.12b","order":"02.39.010.63141"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/micah/4.5"},"Micah 4:5"],"."]]}
